 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130424215057/http://www.americanchronicle.com/articles/view/90756 
 |archivedate=2013-04-24 
 |deadurl=yes 
 }}</ref>，不過他在同年的5月26日被球會放棄<ref>{{en}}{{cite web 
 |url=http://web.mlsnet.com/news/team_news.jsp?ymd=20090526&content_id=4967168&vkey=pr_sje&fext=.jsp&team=t110 
 |title=Earthquakes sign Cornell Glen 
 |publisher=聖荷西地震 
